<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="content-block">
    <h2>How Your Support Helps</h2>
    <p>Over the years, community support has enabled G.R.A.Y. to complete projects that benefit thousands of young athletes across Union County, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Acquiring the Riveria Activity Center for community youth sports</li>
      <li>Improving safety at school athletic fields</li>
      <li>Preparing new baseball and soccer fields at Pioneer Park</li>
      <li>Purchasing shared equipment like top dressing machines for valley fields</li>
      <li>Building new facilities like the La Grande High School Freshman Baseball Field</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Member Organizations</h2>
    <p>G.R.A.Y. serves as the umbrella organization for nine local youth sports programs, including Little League, Babe Ruth Baseball, Legion Baseball, ASA Softball, Youth Soccer, AAU Basketball, Optimist Football, and Union County School Districts Athletics. Your support benefits all of these programs and the young athletes they serve.</p>
  </div>
</section>

